---
import AppLayout from '../layouts/AppLayout.astro';
---

<AppLayout title="Gun 3 - CV Lens Hazirlik">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="panel">
      <p class="eyebrow">Gun 3 - Bizim projeye hazirlik</p>
      <h1>Astro SSR ile mini auth akisi</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Bu uygulama CV Lens'e gecmeden once ihtiyacimiz olan server-side render, API route,
        React island, form handling ve env mantigini tek pratik akista toplar.
      </p>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="button primary" href="/login">Demo girise git</a>
        <a class="button" href="/dashboard">Korumali paneli dene</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <aside class="stack" aria-label="Gun 3 konu ozeti">
      <div class="metric">
        <strong>SSR</strong>
        <span>Sayfalar server'da kosar; cookie kontrolu dashboard render edilmeden yapilir.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="metric">
        <strong>/api</strong>
        <span>Login, logout ve mevcut kullanici bilgisi endpointlerden yonetilir.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="metric">
        <strong>React</strong>
        <span>Astro sayfasinin icinde hydrate edilen kucuk bir oturum durum componenti var.</span>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </section>
</AppLayout>
